      <title>塞内加尔计划到 2027 年将预算赤字削减至十年来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/senegal-aims-to-cut-budget-deficit-to-lowest-in-a-decade-by-2027</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔总理奥斯曼·松科表示，塞内加尔计划从明年开始削减政府开支并寻找增加税收的方法，到 2027 年将预算赤字削减至国内生产总值的 3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-27/senegal-aims-to-cut-budget-deficit-to-lowest-in-a-decade-by-2027</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Dec 2024 19:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
